    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund increased housing provision for homeless people",
        "additional_details": "The Government need to act upon this issue and step in to help those in need especially during this global pandemic as the homeless are amongst the most vulnerable to this virus.\r\n \r\nWe ask the Government to provide the funding necessary to provide housing for all homeless people. Getting the people on the street safe and providing them shelter. The homelessness people deserve a second chance in life and we should give them one.",
        "background": "The Government should be able to ensure housing for the homeless community to keep them off the streets and safe. This would be a simple yet effective plan that would benefit thousands of people and overall improve our community.",
